.TH TWEETA-DESKTOP 1 "29 December 2025" "tweeta-desktop" "Tweeta User Manual"
.SH NAME
tweeta-desktop \- A minimal GTK3 X11 client for Tweetapus
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tweeta-desktop
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tweeta-desktop
is a desktop client for the Tweetapus social media platform. It provides a minimal GTK3 interface to view public timelines, search for users and posts, and manage your Tweetapus account.
.PP
Key features include:
.IP \(bu 2
Viewing public timelines.
.IP \(bu 2
User authentication (Login/Logout).
.IP \(bu 2
Composing and replying to tweets.
.IP \(bu 2
Searching for posts and users.
.IP \(bu 2
Direct messaging between users.
.IP \(bu 2
Viewing user profiles and their tweet history.
.SH OPTIONS
.B tweeta-desktop
accepts standard GTK+ command-line options. For a complete list, see the GTK+ documentation.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/tweeta-desktop/session.json
Stores the session token and username after a successful login.
